lines.text: The right thyroid lobe measures 5.4 x 1.6 x 1.6 cm.
The left thyroid lobe measures 4.9 x 1.6 x 1.3 cm.
The thyroid gland is normal in size with a heterogeneous hypervascular echotexture. No
discrete thyroid nodule is identified. No worrisome cervical lymph nodes.
